Meteorol, Hamburg, Germany; Sacks, W.J., Effects of global irrigation on the near-surface climate (2008) Clim. Dyn., 31, pp. 107-124. , doi:10.1007/s00382-007-0341-y; Seetaramayya, P., Parasnis, S.S., Nagar, S.G., Vernekar, K.G., Thermodynamic structure of the boundary layer in relation to a monsoon depresssion over the Bay of Bengal - A case study (1993) Boundary-Layer Meteorology, 65 (3), pp. 307-314; Siebert, S., Development and validation of the global map of irrigation areas (2005) Hydrol. Earth Syst. Sci., 9, pp. 535-547; Singh, D., Bhadram, C.V.V., Mandal, G.S., New regression model for Indian summer monsoon rainfall (1995) Meteorol. Atmos. Phys., 55, pp. 77-86. , doi:10.1007/BF01029603; Uppala, S.M., The ERA-40 re-analysis (2005) Q. J. R. Meteorol. Soc., 131, pp. 2961-3012. , doi:10.1256/qj.04.176; Willmott, C.J., Matsuura, K., (2009) Terrestrial Precipitation: 1900-2008 Gridded Monthly Time Series (1900-2008), , http://climate.geog.udel.edu, Univ. of Del., Newark","Saeed, F.; Max Planck Institute for Meteorology, Bundesstrasse 53, D-20146 Hamburg, Germany; email: fahad.saeed@zmaw.de",,,,,,,,00948276,,GPRLA,,"English","Geophys. Res. Lett.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-72149128903
